          content: "---\ntype: \"feature\"\ntitle: \"Add database and auth\"\nlogoUrl: \"https://www.gstatic.com/mobilesdk/250721_mobilesdk/mono_firebase_dark.svg\"\n---\n\nYou MUST connect the app to Firebase. Add functionality that uses Google Sign-in with Firebase Auth to securely identify users, and add data persistence to keep track of user data with Firestore."
        }
      }
    }
    items {
      item {
        text_block {
          content: "---\ntype: \"feature\"\ntitle: \"Create & edit images\"\nicon: \"image_edit_auto\"\n---\n\nAdd functionality to the app for users to use text prompts to create or edit images using gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview."
        }
      }
    }
    items {
      item {
        text_block {
          content: "---\ntype: \"feature\"\ntitle: \"Animate images into video\"\nicon: \"movie\"\n---\n\nYou MUST add the ability for users to upload a photo and then generate a video using Veo video generations. Use model: veo-3.1-fast-generate-preview, the generated video must have an aspect ratio of `16:9` (landscape) or `9:16` (portrait)."
        }
      }
    }
    items {
      item {
        text_block {
          content: "---\ntype: \"feature\"\ntitle: \"Generate video from text\"\nicon: \"video_spark\"\n---\n\nYou MUST add Veo 3 video generation to the app using the model veo-3.1-fast-generate-preview, the generated video must have an aspect ratio of `16:9` (landscape) or `9:16` (portrait)."
        }
      }
    }
    items {
      item {
        text_block {
          content: "---\ntype: \"feature\"\ntitle: \"Enable high thinking\"\nicon: \"network_intelligence\"\n---\n\nYou MUST add thinking mode to the app where relevant to handle users\' most complex queries. You MUST use the gemini-3.1-pro-preview model and set `thinkingLevel` to `ThinkingLevel.HIGH`. Do not set `maxOutputTokens`."
        }
      }
    }
