  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Analyzing Project Parameters**\n\nI\'m currently focused on defining the project\'s scope. My initial assessment centers on the provided PDFs, specifically the \"Brand Deck of PraNam Cafe.\" I\'m extracting key information about \"PraNam Cafe\" and \"The Jagmal Group\". I\'m determining the core features of a contactless ordering system. I\'m prioritizing user experience and efficient ordering flow.\n\n\n**Defining Brand Visuals**\n\nI\'ve been solidifying the color palette. \"Sacred Blue\" and \"Earthen Umber\" are primary, with a dark canvas providing contrast. \"Sacred Ivory\" offers a warm light background option. The mission is \"A Curated Journey Along The Sacred Corridors of India.\" We\'re aiming for a polished, premium aesthetic, reflecting the \"100% Vegan-Forward\" focus with dishes from UP\'s cities. The design will use imagery like blue pottery and Mughal motifs.\n\n\n**Exploring Menu Item Details**\n\nI\'m now diving into the menu specifics. I\'m focusing on the descriptions and details of the Varanasi items, particularly from PDF 2. I\'m noting the ingredients, pricing, and categorizations like \"Heritage\" or \"Chef\'s Pick\". I\'m getting a feel for the dish presentation. I\'m focused on the \"Ghaat\'s Golden Embrace,\" \"Tikki Durbar,\" \"Spinach Fritters,\" and \"The Bitter Jewel of Banaras.\"\n\n\n**Cataloging Menu Offerings**\n\nI\'m currently compiling menu item details with pricing and descriptions. I\'ve noted \"Tamatar Chaat\" and various lassi and chaas options. I\'m also cataloging the \"Clouds of Kashi\" dessert. In the Prayagraj category, I\'ve added \"Sangam Samosa Ragda.\" My priority is to create a complete and organized list.\n\n\n**Compiling Menu Items**\n\nI\'ve added new breakfast items to the menu, including descriptions, pricing, and classifications like \"Heritage\" or \"Chef\'s Pick\". I\'ve included details on \"Khasta with Dum Aloo,\" \"Grand Kachori Thali,\" \"Yogurt Dumplings,\" \"Saffron Coil & Cream,\" \"Rose Spheres,\" and the \"Marble City Breakfast.\" My focus remains on completing the catalog of offerings.\n\n\n**Adding Menu Updates**\n\nI\'ve just added three Mughlai Paratha variants to the catalog, noting their descriptions and pricing. I\'ve also incorporated Ivory Sweetmeat options, both dry and in syrup, with descriptions. I\'m moving on to Mathura-region items, including a Golden Gram Crepe and a Green Lentil Veil, with detailed descriptions. Finally, I\'ve begun to add items from Muradabad, specifically The Brass City\'s Lentil Banquet. I am prioritizing a complete menu inventory.\n\n\n**Incorporating Menu Details**\n\nI\'ve just added several items to the menu inventory, specifically from the \"Lucknow\" and \"Beverages\" sections. This includes the \"Homestyle Bowl\" with detailed ingredients, pricing, and descriptions. I\'m noting the \"Golden Cradle\" basket chaat and the \"Royal Biryani\" from Lucknow. I\'ve also incorporated the \"coolcool Shikanji\" and the \"Namkeen Sattu\" drinks, ensuring complete descriptions and pricing for each entry.\n\n\n**Defining System Functionality**\n\nI\'m now integrating system features. Illustrations and animations are essential, so I\'m considering using the `image-generation` tool. I must read `SKILL.md` for that tool first. I am also working on payment integration with mock credit card and UPI options, and a QR code generator for a seamless contactless experience, and integrating a Gemini AI chatbot.\n\n\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 9
      nanos: 798236399
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
