          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    history: \"A staple across Northern India. In Varanasi, the \'water bomb\' is famous for its intensive infusion of mint, coriander, ginger, rock-salt, and cooling digestive elixirs.\","
