  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Confirming Source Data**\n\nI\'ve confirmed the successful creation of `/src/data/menu.ts`. The file now houses all menu items, complete with accurate details like names, prices, origin cities, histories, vegan alternatives, and even vector illustrations. The data structures are comprehensive, now ready for implementation.\n\n\n**Implementing Server Routes**\n\nI\'m now fully immersed in server-side implementation! The `server.ts` file is taking shape. I\'ve successfully incorporated necessary imports for Express, path, and Google\'s GenAI SDK. The `/api/chat` endpoint is set up, ready to invoke `generateContent` using the `\'gemini-3.5-flash\'` model. I\'m also planning for development and production modes, and have also added plans for simulating contactless table check-in.\n\n\n**Developing Frontend Functionality**\n\nI\'m now focusing on the frontend user experience. I\'m selecting items, integrating a vegan switch, and managing quantities. I\'m also planning the chat interface for AI recommendations, ready to generate queries like \"Should I get Tamatar Chaat?\". I am also developing the checkout flow, with UPI simulation, order tracking, and receipt generation. The current server will handle raw JSON from requests using Express.\n\n\n"
