  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Verifying Server Functionality**\n\nExcellent! The Node.js server rebooted without issue. I\'m now cross-checking to ensure no further adjustments are required at this stage. We\'re on track after the restart. I have just confirmed we have a contactless restaurant system in progress, intended for \"PraNam Cafe\".\n\n\n**Designing Visual Harmony**\n\nI\'ve been immersed in crafting a visually rich experience. The color scheme incorporating \"Sacred Blue\" and \"Earthen Umber,\" along with the luxury cultural philosophy, is shaping up beautifully, mirroring the brand\'s authentic slide deck. I\342\200\231m focusing on cover pages, watermarks, and font combinations (Cinzel, Inter & JetBrains Mono) to produce premium layouts.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have successfully designed and built the contactless restaurant ordering system for **PraNam Cafe**, adhering strictly to the branding, regional roots, culinary legacy, and visual assets detailed in your brand deck and menu. \n\nHere is a design and functional overview of what has been implemented:\n\n### \360\237\216\250 Premium Visual Identity & Typography\n* **The \"Sacred Blue & Earthen Gold\" Theme:** Styled with elements of **Sacred Blue** (`#1AACBF`), **Earthen Umber** (`#B8963E`), and **Deep Night** (`#0B1317`) dark marble backdrops, mirroring the brand deck.\n* **Aesthetic Pairings:** Imported of Google\'s **Cinzel** (serif) for the display headers to convey heritage and ancient majesty, paired with **Inter** for legible content and **JetBrains Mono** for pricing/numerical tables.\n* **100% Vegan-Forward Commitment:** Embedded a prominent **\"100% Plant-Based\"** toggle systemwide (and per item). Customers can instantly convert any dish to use non-dairy substitutes (e.g., *almond sweet curd, cashew-coconut rabri, tofu-paneer, plant butter*).\n\n### \360\237\215\233 Curated Uttar Pradesh Regional Menu\nThe catalog features your authentic dishes categorized across five of Uttar Pradesh\'s most sacred corridors (loaded with prices, native names, and descriptions):\n* **Varanasi (Kashi):** *The Ghaat\'s Golden Embrace* (Aloo Kachori), *Tikki Durbar* (Aloo Tikki), and *Clouds of Kashi* (the rare cardamom sweet *Dudh Malaiyo* dried overnight under winter dew).\n* **Prayagraj (Sangam):** *Sangam Samosa Ragda*, *The Pilgrim\'s Breakfast* (Khasta Dum Aloo), and *Saffron Coil & Cream* (Crisp Hot Jalebi with cold Rabdi).\n* **Agra (City of Taj):** *The Marble City Breakfast* (Bedhai Puri) and the historic *Ivory Sweetmeats* (legendary crispy and syrupy Pethas).\n* **Mathura (Brij):** Fresh pastoral *Golden Gram Crepes* (Besan Chilla) and *Green Lentil Veils* (Moong Dal Chilla).\n* **Muradabad (Brass City):** *The Brass City\'s Lentil Banquet* (Muradabadi Moong Dal with crushed papadums) served in simulated brassware bowls.\n* **Lucknow (Nawab):** *Golden Cradle* ( Hazraganj\'s layered Basket Tokri Chaat) and the fragrant slow-cooked *Royal Awadhi Dum Biryani*.\n\n### \360\237\216\250 Illustrations & Micro-Animations\n* **Custom Vector Illustrations:** Every single dish features a beautifully styled, distinct SVG vector illustration embedded natively. \n* **Tactile Motion Effects:** Hovering over any dish scales the dish, turns it slightly, and activates **floating hot steam draft particles** ascending above fresh items! Detailed, slide-down collapsible storytelling panels reveal the culinary history of each dish.\n\n### \360\237\222\263 Integrated Contactless Payment Portal\n* **Table Scanned Context:** Auto-reads physical table numbers from URL query parameters (e.g., `?table=4`), keeping the interface directly linked to the layout.\n* **Dual Checkout Flow:**\n  1. **BHARAT UPI QR Code:** Generates a coordinate-precise secure QR code for GPay/PhonePe and handles status verifying loaders.\n  2. **Loyalty Card Terminal:** Fully mock-interactive bank credit card display validating number digits, cardholder name, expirations, and secure CVVs.\n* **Torn Receipts:** On successful payments, a retro physical ticket with realistic torn zig-zag edges compiles items, quantities, table information, and calculated totals.\n\n### \360\237\215\263 Active Kitchen Order Queue Tracker\n* Places a prominent live cooking status panel above the catalog upon order placement.\n* Steps guests through active cooking cycles: **Spices Assembly** \342\236\224 **Wood-Fire Dum / Griddling** \342\236\224 **Plating & Saffron Garnishes** \342\236\224 **Delivered to Table in porous clay Kulhads**.\n\n### \360\237\222\254 AI-Powered Culinary Host Chatbot (Saras)\n* Integrated a server-side floating chat widget powered by the secure `@google/genai` SDK and the `gemini-3.5-flash` model.\n* Converses as the hospitable host **Saras**, welcoming guests with polite local phrasing (\"*Pranam! Aapka swagat hai* \360\237\231\217\"), describing the historical origin of dishes, explaining how plant-based dairy substitutes are processed, and guiding them to checkout.\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 2
      nanos: 290840329
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
